2024-02-01 13:19:35 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1706793575,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"89.23.103.188","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 12_5) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/114.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36 OPR\/89.0.4447.51","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":9893,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"3","project_id":"834","nick":"Reina","topic":"studioatrium Leads","content":"Hi studioatrium\r\n\r\nWe are proud to present our new website for all your B2B and B2C data and advertising needs. \r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/studioatrium.marketingfriend.biz\r\n\r\nWe offer a large range of products and to assist you in getting ahead this new yeah with better advertising and reaching more clients in your specific niche. Our products include all of the following: \r\n\r\nWe provide a free live search on site so you can see the amount and type of data we provide.\r\nPre-compiled B2B and B2C data sets with all the necessary fieldscolumns included to assist you reach your clients.\r\nIf we do not currently have the data you are looking for we are also willing to assist with custom data collection.\r\nMail servers setup for you able to send over a million mails per day or as per your specifications.\r\n\r\n\u201cStopping advertising to save money is like stopping your watch to save time.\u201d Henry Ford. \r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/studioatrium.marketingfriend.biz\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nMarketingFriend.biz","create_date":"2024-02-01 13:19:35","modify_date":"2024-02-01 13:19:35","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2532655},"entity_changes":false}
