2024-02-12 12:03:19 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1707739399,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"178.214.5.5","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:122.0) Gecko\/20100101 Firefox\/122.0","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":9911,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"3","project_id":"1380","nick":"Marcin","topic":"Materia\u0142y i szacunkowe koszty","content":"Witam, czy jest mo\u017cliwo\u015b\u0107 otrzymania szacunkowych koszt\u00f3w budowy\/materia\u0142\u00f3w projektu Roberto? Prawdopodobnie b\u0119dziemy budowa\u0107 ten dom jednak zastanawiamy si\u0119 nad pewnymi zmianami i najpierw chcemy zobaczy\u0107 og\u00f3lne zestawienie a p\u00f3\u017aniej kombinowa\u0107. Je\u015bli kto\u015b stawia\u0142 ten dom to mo\u017ce si\u0119 pochwali\u0107 realizacj\u0105 gotowego :) \r\nsiono1991@op.pl","create_date":"2024-02-12 12:03:19","modify_date":"2024-02-12 12:03:19","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2537263},"entity_changes":false}
